OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy at first in the far
OL,6,Fsoutheast with light rain or drizzle,
OL,7,Fsoon clearing. Mostly dry elsewhere
OL,8,Fwith sunny spells. Cloud and rain
OL,9,Fspread into the northwest later, snow
OL,10,Fon Scottish hills, turning windy with
OL,11,Fpossible coastal gales. Average
OL,12,Ftemperatures.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FCloud, rain or drizzle move
OL,15,Fsoutheastwards, reaching most areas by
OL,16,Fdawn, though the far southeast staying
OL,17,Fdry. Snow affects Scottish hills.
OL,18,FIncreasingly windy with possible
OL,19,Fnorthern coastal gales.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
