OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FRain spreads southeastwards
OL,6,Fwhich can be heavy on western hills.
OL,7,FBrighter, showery weather follows into
OL,8,Fnorthern Scotland. Windy for many,
OL,9,Fwith gusts near high ground. Mild
OL,10,Fsouth, colder north.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
